title: World of Warcraft Comics Vol. 1 - 4
description:
World of Warcraft Comics Vol. 1 - 4
Inspired by the outrageously popular MMORPG!

Volume 1: A human is found unconscious on the shores of Kalimdor, with no memory of who he is or how he arrived there. Enslaved by the Orc Shaman, Rehgar Earthfury, this man must fight for survival against members of both the Alliance and the Horde, striking uneasy relationships with other races in his quest to find the secrets of his past!
#00 - Prologue
#01 - Stranger in a Strange Land
#02 - Killing Ground
#03 - Destiny Awaits!
#04 - Balancing the Scales
#05 - The Beast Within!
#06 - Blood
#07 - Revelations

Volume 2: The second collection, tells the saga of the Missing King of Stormwind. Upon learning he is in fact the lost ruler of Stormwind, Lo'Gosh returns to reclaim his throne with his comrades-in-arms Valeera and Broll. But all is not as it seems in the Eastern Kingdom, especially if one informed dwarf has anything to say about it.
#08 - The Return
#09 - Through the Mirror Darkly
#10 - Last of the Line
#11 - Descent
#12 - The Enemy Revealed
#13 - Flashback
#14 - Into the Jaws of Death!

Volume 3: As the Horde and the Alliance continue to seek diplomatic peace, the assassin of Varian's father, Garona Halforcen, once again appears to disturb negotiations, and what role will her son play in the world of Azeroth?
#15 - Conflicting Loyalties
#16 - Threat!
#17 - Gathering Thunder!
#18 - Showdown!
#19 - The Winds of War
#20 - Repercussions
#21 - Secrets

Volume 4: A new Council of Tirisfal is formed following an attempt on Med'an's life. And while Med'an, Valeera and Maraad travel to Kharazhan to speak with the shade of Med'an's father, Garona and Meryl team up to take out the ogre Cho'gall.
#22 - Whispers
#23 - The Gathering
#24 - Hard Choices
#25 - Armageddon

All files in .cbr format

Missing Ashbringer & Beginnings and Ends

Ashbringer
World of Warcraft: Ashbringer recounts the story of the Ashbringer and Alexandros Mograine.
1 Death is Contagious
2 Ashes to Ashes
3 Naxxramas
4 Dust to Dust

Beginnings and Ends
World of Warcraft: Beginnings and Ends is a one-shot special issue that introduced new Alliance and Horde characters that had not been seen in the ongoing series.
